desc: Holland Beauty, A leading wholesale Flower Bulbs Supplier Company since 1975. Shop online quality Tulip Bulbs, Hyacinths, Daffodils, Crocus and Calla Lily Bulb.

layout.text: Holland Beauty Flower & Bulb Corporation imports and distributes spring and fall planting flower bulbs

Our products include tulips, daffodils, hyacinths, crocus, allium, packaged amaryllis and paperwhites, lilies, dahlias, cannas, callas, gladioli, and begonias. Holland Beauty sells its products through retail stores, including garden centers, nurseries, hardware stores, grocery stores and landscapers. The company was founded in 1975 with main office and production facilities located in Milwaukee, Wisconsin.
